{"type": "article", "id": 13159, "title": "一根表带两块表", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-07T07:28:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000252McdYtLoIZTahqmwv.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t有人痴迷智能科技的酷炫，有人执著于传统工艺的优雅，来自硅谷的 Nico Gerard 则干脆把两者做到了一块儿手表上，这款叫做 “Pinnacle+Apple Watch” 的手表正面是传统瑞士表，背面则安装了一个 38mm 的 Apple Watch 表盘，这下你的手腕正面背面都闲不着了。这款手表目前有银色和金色两种款式可以选择，已经投入生产。不过，我们一直觉得贪心的设计往往容易陷入尴尬，不妨继续观望一下。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140800LZdt3eOogTwuNJns.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140800xDuiB6JSz15WbTjl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53178484\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261408016zEwAqlsyN9pOi1T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140801yosw1z3APELXrF0U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261408018GrFgT4EsebRz2vP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}